  "description": "<p><strong>Job Vacancy: Construction Carpenter</strong></p><p><strong>Company:</strong> SUN LIKE\nENGINEERING HANDYMEN PTE. LTD.<br />\n<strong>Position:</strong> Construction Carpenter<br />\n<strong>Employment Type:</strong> Full-Time<br />\n<strong>Experience Required:</strong> Minimum 5 Years</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform carpentry works for construction\n     and renovation projects</li><li>Fabricate and install wooden structures\n     including doors, frames, cabinets, partitions, and formwork</li><li>Interpret and work according to\n     construction drawings and measurements</li><li>Carry out repair, maintenance, and\n     modification work as required</li><li>Operate carpentry tools and machinery\n     safely and efficiently</li><li>Coordinate with site supervisors and other\n     trades on site</li><li>Ensure work quality meets project\n     requirements and timelines</li><li>Comply with site safety regulations and\n     company policies</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>At least 5 years of relevant experience as\n     a construction carpenter</li><li>Hands-on experience in site carpentry,\n     renovation, or building works</li><li>Able to work independently with minimal\n     supervision</li><li>Physically fit and comfortable working on\n     construction sites</li><li>Responsible, hardworking, and a good team\n     player</li></ul>",
